track.name: EVERY CHANCE I GET (feat. Lil Baby & Lil Durk)

wiki.summary: “EVERY CHANCE I GET” is the 2nd track on DJ Khaled’s 12th studio album KHALED KHALED. It is produced by Tennessee based Tay Keith and it features Atlanta rapper Lil Baby and Chicago rapper Lil Durk. While Khaled and Baby had collabed on two different occasions prior to this on You Stay and Weather the Storm, this is the first collab between Khaled and Durk. Lil Baby and Durk however, have numerous collaborations to their names and there is even a joint mixtape between them being teased to be released soon. Read more on Last.fm.
